manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Easy setup in 4 steps： 1. Plug the extender into a power outlet near your router. Wait about 20s until the first power-on light of the Repeater slowly flash; 2. Go to your phone's WiFi connection page and select "Repeater-XXX" to connect. (If you can't find the name of the repeater WIFI, it is recommended to turn on Airplane Mode on your phone and then turn off Airplane Mode.) ； 3. Connect to "Repeater-XXX" and then jump directly to the browser page to set the WIFI information of the repeater, note that the repeater password set inside needs to be the same as the router's WIFI password!!! If you can't jump automatically, enter 192.168.11.1 in this browser; 4. If it still doesn't work, there is another way, you can plug in the Internet cable through the computer and enter the IP address (192.168.11.1) on the computer browser to configure.

FAQ: 1. Q：How do I reset the Extender A : To reset the extender,use the reset pin to press the RESET button for 10-15 seconds to restore factory setttings.The WiFi SSID of the wifi extender will be "Repeater-xxxx" after restoring successfully.Then set up again from the beginning. 2. Q : Dose the Extender work with 5G? A:No, the extender only operates in the 2.4Ghz band. 3. Q : I can't see WiFi Extender in my network list. A : Please press the RESET button for 15 seconds, and wait 30 seconds. The power indicator will flash quickly. Then check the network list one more time. 4. Q : I tried to open your IP address, but it says no internet or page error. A : Please open your Wi-Fi settings and check your network. You need to be connected to the Extender network, not to the main router or mobile internet network! You will have a “no internet” connection near the network “Repeater-xxxx”, but it’s correct! Until you finish setup, the network will be without internet. NOTE: You can’t connect to the IP or site, when you have an internet connection because this is not an internet page, but the setting page of your Extender. 5. Q : When I’m connected to Wi-Fi Extender, it says no internet. A : This issue you have is because of the wrong password.Even if you are sure about the correct password. pease reset your device and set it up again

Special Problem Q:What should i do if i cannot access the repeater's web management page? A: 1.Make sure your computer is connected to the extended networl 2.Make sure your conputer is set to obtain an IP address automatically 3.If the Repeater has connected to the router ,you should go to your router's DHCP client list to obtain the Repeater's current IP address Reset the Repeater Q:Why does the wireless transmission rate speed down,when the wireless signal is stronger after repeated by the Repeater? A: In compliance with the wireless transmission protocol,all the repeater devices are set to work in half-duplex instead of full-duplex mode. In other words,the repeater has to process one-way communication between your root wireless router(or AP) and the terminal clients,so the transmission time will be double-increased ,while the speed will be decreased.Recommends that you reset the extender when your home network connection is poor,or when you want a larger wireless coverage to eliminate"dead zones" Q:Why the devices connected to the Repeater cannot get an IP address from the Repeater and cannot access the Internet A: 1.Maybe your enabled a wireless MAC filter,wireless access control,or access control list(ACL) on your router. To solve this problem,please log into your router.To solve this problem,please log into your and disable the mac filter, wireless access acontrol or ACL 2.Maybe the Repeater has not been successfully connected to your router,please reset the Repeater and reconfiguration 3.Maybe the IP address of the router is occupied or the wireless device connected by the router has reached the limit.plsease reboot your router,then reset the Repeater and Reconfiguration

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The WiFi Extender with its 4 Super Antennas is a game-changer for anyone seeking a robust and extended Wi-Fi range at home. This booster effortlessly amplifies signals with its 2.4GHz frequency, effectively erasing dead zones and providing a reliable, high-speed connection throughout the house.The installation is a breeze, and the compact design ensures it blends seamlessly with any home decor. The four super antennas ensure an expanded, uninterrupted coverage area, allowing for smoother streaming, gaming, and overall internet usage without dropouts.If you're in need of a reliable, user-friendly, and highly efficient Wi-Fi booster that significantly improves your home network's reach, this WiFi Extender is an absolute must-have. It's an affordable and effective solution for anyone seeking a stronger and more stable Wi-Fi signal.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super easy to setup. Ethernet plugs are helping.
reviews.reviewText: After I plugged it in and connected to it, it took me a minute to figure out how to access the settings on my phone but after that it was really quick and easy to set up!I'm using it to have my game consoles plugged into Ethernet in my bedroom cuz the Wi-Fi on them aren't great since they're old and this little device has already helped a lot.Before using the Ethernet through the wifi extender I was getting 2-5mbps download speeds on my Xbox one from 2014 and now it's been going all the way up to like 60-70 on average.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Item did not make a difference, no boost to internet
reviews.reviewText: Since receiving this item I've tried everything to get it to work, I tried many different locations throughout the house and/or the garage with no increase or boost to the signal. I even scheduled to have the cable company come out thinking there could be a problem with my internet, the cable company found nothing wrong. I've tried to go to the website listed on the back of the instructions with no luck. I truly hope it will work for someone it did not work for me. I'll list it as one of the items I ordered from Amazon that didn't work and as with other items it will sit on the shelf in the garage until it get discarded.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars This product improved my wifi strength allowing me to connect devices across a 2400 sq ft basement.
reviews.reviewText: I had to log into the device using its IP address to get it to function properly. Once enabled it did a satisfactory job of expanding our existing WIFI network range. It is inexpensive and seems to work as advertised.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This wifi extender was very easy to setup and you don't even need the app.The range was good enough (able to reach the rooms downstairs) and provides good value for the price.It also does not take too long to provide the extender when switched on like some other brands.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works like a charm
reviews.reviewText: Not hard to set up and amplifies the signal a good distance.I moved into an apartment where the signal is strongest along one wall. Everywhere else it is too weak to do anything constructive so I bought this after reading reviews and watching a video on YouTube and I'm glad I made the purchase.Now I don't have to have a secondary phone against the wall to Bluetooth music to my speaker.
